wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>3. Kirkjubaer ii<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In between Vik and the Skaftafell waterfall is Kirkjubaer ii. A campsite with a huge mountain as a backdrop. Like Seljalandsfoss it has a kitchen area, good warm showers. Staying here with a campervan costs 1400 ISK ($13) per person + 300 ISK for a 5-minute shower.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Skaftafell is one of the <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/iceland\/waterfalls-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Most Beautiful Waterfalls in Iceland<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/campsites-iceland-Kirkjubaer-ii.jpg\" alt=\"campsites iceland Kirkjubaer ii\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"329\" alt=\"campsites iceland Kirkjubaer ii\" class=\"wp-image-8039 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153222\/campsites-iceland-Kirkjubaer-ii.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153222\/campsites-iceland-Kirkjubaer-ii-300x220.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153222\/campsites-iceland-Kirkjubaer-ii-600x439.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153222\/campsites-iceland-Kirkjubaer-ii-450x329.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/0