block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>5. Reykjavik<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This might be a strange one but staying on the campsite near Reykjavik is surprisingly good. With just an 8-minute drive to the center of Reykjavik, this campsite is perfect if you want to spend a day or two exploring the city. The campsite offers hot showers and has a mini-supermarket.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The price for staying with a campervan is 1750 ISK ($16.5) per person + 300 ISK for an unlimited hot water shower.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/iceland\/things-to-do-reykjavik\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Must do&#x2019;s in&#xA0;Reykjavik, City Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/campsites-iceland-reykjavik.jpg\" alt=\"campsites iceland reykjavik\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"329\" alt=\"campsites iceland reykjavik\" class=\"wp-image-8043 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153219\/campsites-iceland-reykjavik.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153219\/campsites-iceland-reykjavik-300x219.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhai