 town is surrounded by popular places to visit like Dyrh&#xF3;laey. The campsite is located on the foot of a mountain. It offers cold showers, a kitchen area, WiFi and a supermarket nearby. Price for a campervan is 1750 ISK ($16.5) per person.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/campsites-iceland-vik-church.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8049\" class=\"wp-image-8049 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153211\/campsites-iceland-vik-church-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltino